com.github.wuic.engine
Class EngineRequest

java.lang.Object
  com.github.wuic.engine.EngineRequest

public class EngineRequest
extends Object

This class represents a request to be indicated to an engine.

The user which invokes Engine.parse(EngineRequest) should indicates in the parameter the resources to be parsed and the context path to use to expose the generated resources.

0.3.0
